social_posts.post_text: Thankful for the diverse beauty on Earth ☁️ 🌞🙏🏾💧🌏 🌱#thankyou

I went to the top of little Adams peak. I hiked and panted until I made it to the top. The top was the one of the most beautiful things my eyes have seen. Peace. I was in awe. Beauty in it’s most natural form. I sat on a huge rock at the top of the view and meditated after I meditated , I prayed still with my eyes closed and then again open. I admired in silence. Thanking the most high for blessing me with everything including this view. It was peace. It was beauty. 🤍
Love you in the morning , love you In the night . It’s amazing how much it feels right.
I could have been a pearl
